{"tid":2175684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張超雄: 重新考慮是否延任議員. 無法再與政權溝通","createTime":"2020-08-26T15:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T02:26:29.000Z","uid":134071,"like":669,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"e24339ce1b33bcd79fcd98c6a15405c2dc4c7932","tid":2175684,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"民主黨立法會議員林卓廷及許智峯今早遭警方上門拘捕，林卓廷更被指涉嫌於去年元朗7.21恐襲中參與暴動。民主派立法會議員和民陣傍晚見記者，批評警方顛倒黑白是非。工黨張超雄更明言，今次的濫捕令他重新考慮是否要延任立法會議員，表明無法再繼續與政權溝通。<br />\n<br />\n在記者會上，張超雄表示，警方首次否定7.21恐襲為無差別襲擊，諷警方已正式淪為「警謊」，又指香港警察的做法和立場在國安法下再突變，認為警察已由國安指揮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076818&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=a7242191\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076818&h=99449f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076818</a>"},{"pid":"b8538a8a87c5f87347a9d761e03294f0565f3b7f","tid":2175684,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc22a8d3834fd3be5b369ae0996cc38dab6eae5","tid":2175684,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"新界北總區副指揮官曾正科交代及回應記者元朗721事件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2175647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2175647</a>"},{"pid":"f3164e558ab974a54f14792791d4f073af14961a","tid":2175684,"uid":127575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" 